title: Middle Eastern Aromas Restaurant and Grocery
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Mediterranean, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Catering, Middle Eastern, Lebanese, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Homestyle Lebanese cuisine combined with a grocery store. Family run. Lots of vegetarian and vegan items on menu: salads, wraps, vegetarian combination plate, hummus, grape leaves, foole, baba ghanoush, falafel. All items made fresh daily by the grandmother and grandfather for 22 years. Belly dancer Friday nights.
